Thriftpy-Cli
=============

Install
========

.. code:: bash

    pip install thriftpy-cli

Usage
=====

.. code:: bash

    $ thriftpy-cli -f thrift_file.thrift -h localhost -p 8010 -s ServiceName
    $ # Launching into ipython
    >>> client.api(*args)


